manifests.contents:
bench = []
test = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "mini-app"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "mini-app"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
build = "build.rs"
authors = ["you"]
description = "A Tauri App"
license = ""
repository = ""
rust-version = "1.57"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true

[dependencies]
serde_json = "1.0"

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.tauri]
path = "../../tauri/core/tauri/"

[build-dependencies.tauri-build]
version = "1.4"
features = []

[features]
custom-protocol = ["tauri/custom-protocol"]
default = ["custom-protocol"]
